ChatRoom  
Communication A Communication needs at least two "Actors" which talk to each other, further the Communication is stored into "CommunicationHistory" (together with a "CommunicationItem")
CommunicationContainer This domain object acts as an container to allow the retrieval of Communication History (each history entry connects a Communication and a CommunicationItem)
CommunicationRating A Communication needs at least two "Actors" which talk to each other, further the Communication is stored into "CommunicationHistory" (together with a "CommunicationItem")
Contract It is possible to add a contract to a Negotiation
CP_Actor In the context of "CollaborativePlanning", Actor acts as an NegotiationIssue and further as CommunicationItem, so that it is possible to talk about Actors.
CP_BusinessOpportunity In the context of "CollaborativePlanning", BO acts as an NegotiationIssue and further as CommunicationItem, so that it is possible to talk about BO.
CP_Process In the context of "CollaborativePlanning", Process acts as an NegotiationIssue and further as CommunicationItem, so that it is possible to talk about Processes.
Goal In the context of "CollaborativePlanning", Goal acts as an NegotiationIssue and further as CommunicationItem, so that it is possible to talk about Goals.
Negotiation Negotiation acts as a container due to the negotiation of negotiation items between Actors.
NegotiationConstraint This domain objects acts as an value container, which allows to add constraints to NegotiationIssues
NegotiationIssue NegotiationIssue acts as an superclass for Actor, Relation, Process, Responsibility, Goal and BO.
NegotiationItem A NegotiationItem acts as a container, which has a Negotiation, a NegotiationIssue and a arbitrary number of Offers.
Offer An offer has one ore more NegotiationItems and one Actor.
Relation In the context of "CollaborativePlanning", Relation acts as an NegotiationIssue and further as CommunicationItem, so that it is possible to talk about Relations.
Responsibility In the context of "CollaborativePlanning", Responsibility acts as an NegotiationIssue and further as CommunicationItem, so that it is possible to talk about Responsibility.
Topic  
TopicRating  
Valuation A Valuation concerns a certain Actor and an arbitrary number of "NegotiationIssues".
